Bobbie Brown https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bobbie_Brown 0 Bobbie Jean Brown (born October 7, 1969), sometimes credited as Bobbie Brown-Lane, is an American actress, model and former beauty pageant contestant. She appeared in the video for Warrant's glam metal anthem "Cherry Pie" and the cover of the album of the same name.
